        Reads MIME content from a document into a Writer in a streaming fashion.
        Parameters:
        doc - document to read MIME
        itemName - name of item for the MIME content (e.g. "body")
        dataType - specifies with MIME data types should be read
        targetWriter - writer to receive the MIME content
